content:
{
  "action": "use_tool",
  "tool_name": "write_file",
  "payload": {
    "path": "course_outline_slides.html",
    "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>AI大模型（AIGC）赋能企业创新 - 课程幻灯片</title>
<style>
  body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a3a6c 0%, #2980b9 100%);
    color: white;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .slide {
    display: none;
    width: 100vw;
    height: 100vh;
    padding: 60px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
  }
  .slide.active {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .title {
    font-size: 3em;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  }
  .content {
    font-size: 1.5em;
    max-width: 800px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .icon {
    font-size: 4em;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .decoration {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 20px;
    right: 20px;
    font-size: 2em;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }
  .nav {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 30px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    z-index: 100;
  }
  .nav button {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    border: none;
    color: white;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    margin: 0 10px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 1em;
  }
  .nav button:hover {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="slide active" id="slide1">
  <div class="icon">🤖</div>
  <div class="title">《AI大模型（AIGC）赋能企业创新》</div>
  <div class="content">
    <p>中高管战略决策与业务落地工作坊 - 1天浓缩版课程</p>
    <p>时长：1天（6小时） | 学员：企业中高级管理人员</p>
  </div>
  <div class="decoration">✨</div>
</div>

<div class="slide" id="slide2">
  <div class="icon">🧠</div>
  <div class="title">模块1：认知革命</div>
  <div class="content">
    <p>AI大模型本质与产业影响</p>
    <p>AIGC重塑企业价值链</p>
    <p>形式：主题演讲+行业案例视频</p>
    <p>目标：破除技术迷雾，建立战略级认知</p>
  </div>
  <div class="decoration">🎯</div>
</div>

<div class="slide" id="slide3">
  <div class="icon">🛠️</div>
  <div class="title">模块2：核心武器库</div>
  <div class="content">
    <p>高管必备AI驱动能力</p>
    <p>提示工程：用自然语言指挥AI的思维模型</p>
    <p>业务自动化：核心武器库工具使用</p>
    <p>实战案例：汇报材料自动化、数据整理自动化、图形图像自动化</p>
    <p>形式：互动演练+小组讨论</p>
    <p>目标：掌握AI驱动方法，理解自动化边界</p>
  </div>
  <div class="decoration">💡</div>
</div>

<div class="slide" id="slide4">
  <div class="icon">📊</div>
  <div class="title">模块3：业务落地沙盘</div>
